{"id":292039,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/global-voices-孟加拉发声终结对女性的暴力行为/","date":"2013-05-05T06:15:15Z","modified":"2013-05-05T06:15:15Z","title":"Global Voices | 孟加拉发声终结对女性的暴力行为","content":"<p><p>上周全国有上千名孟加拉人上街游行，呐喊着“够了、够了”，要求终结对女性的暴力行为。这次游行是“<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.onebillionrising.org/\">亿触即发</a>”（One Billion Rising）活动的一部份。</p>\n<p>全世界有<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.vday.org/node/3040\">203</a>个国家于2013年2月14日组织反暴力示威活动，孟加拉为其中之一。孟加拉全部64个县，超过<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://twitter.com/OBRBangladesh/status/301998063780761600\">1万3000人</a>“站”出来抗争。</p>\n<p>对于南亚的国家人民而言，“亿触即发”活动有很大的作用。当地警方指出，2011年至2012年间，据报有17万4691名孟加拉女性为暴力受害者，他们所受到的暴力包括硫酸攻击、诱拐绑架、强奸、谋杀、毒品交易与谋取嫁妆。</p>\n<p>根据“联合国人类发展报告”，孟加拉是<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.newagebd.com/supliment.php?sid=126&#038;id=922\">该地区发生最多强奸事件的国家</a>，这表示大约1000个人里面就有一位女性遭强奸。</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/OneBillionRisingBangladesh\">“亿触即发”</a>是“<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.vday.org/home\">V-Day</a>”运动中最大型的全球行动，其命名源自联合国的统计，全球至少有10亿女性一生中曾遭遇过性或生理上的暴力。</p>\n<p>以下是来自<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/media/set/?set=a.170778413059322.42026.154744967996000&#038;type=1\">“亿触即发”的脸书页面</a>，此次活动的照片。</p>\n<p> </p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=235884599882036&#038;set=a.235376876599475.60209.154744967996000&#038;type=3&#038;src=http%3A%2F%2Fsphotos-b.ak.fbcdn.net%2Fhphotos-ak-prn1%2F17711_235884599882036_983115160_n.jpg&#038;size=960%2C640\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-35471\" alt=\"Parliamentarians solidarity with One Billion Rising campaign\" src=\"http://bn.globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/Parliamentarians-RISING-375x250.jpg\" width=\"375\" height=\"250\" /></a></p>\n<p>国会议员声援“亿触即发”活动</p>\n</div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=502492519793504&#038;set=a.500914299951326.111933.117082028334557&#038;type=3&#038;theater\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-35472\" alt=\"Action Aid Bangladesh's protesting violence against women by singing. \" src=\"http://bn.globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/aid-cap-2-375x250.jpg\" width=\"375\" height=\"250\" /></a></p>\n<p>“行动援助孟加拉”（Action Aid Bangladesh）透过歌曲，反对对女性施暴的行为</p>\n</div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=235380879932408&#038;set=a.235376876599475.60209.154744967996000&#038;type=3&#038;src=http%3A%2F%2Fsphotos-c.ak.fbcdn.net%2Fhphotos-ak-prn1%2F21704_235380879932408_274187408_n.jpg&#038;size=640%2C480\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-35473\" alt=\"Garments workers RISING in Gulshan, Dhaka.\" src=\"http://bn.globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/Garments-workers-RISING-in-Dhaka-375x281.jpg\" width=\"375\" height=\"281\" /></a></p>\n<p>达卡市（Dhaka）玫瑰园地区（Gulshan）的制衣厂工人声援反对对女性施暴的行为</p>\n</div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=235568283247001&#038;set=a.235376876599475.60209.154744967996000&#038;type=3&#038;src=http%3A%2F%2Fsphotos-b.ak.fbcdn.net%2Fhphotos-ak-prn1%2F539461_235568283247001_1346513312_n.jpg&#038;size=960%2C720\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-35474\" alt=\"Men and women from small town Sirajgonj RISING. \" src=\"http://bn.globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/539461_235568283247001_1346513312_n-375x281.jpg\" width=\"375\" height=\"281\" /></a></p>\n<p>小城镇Sirajgonj的人们也都站出来</p>\n</div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=236082889862207&#038;set=a.235376876599475.60209.154744967996000&#038;type=3&#038;src=http%3A%2F%2Fsphotos-b.ak.fbcdn.net%2Fhphotos-ak-ash4%2F379321_236082889862207_1155520113_n.jpg&#038;size=960%2C619\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-35475\" alt=\"UN showed their solidarity.\" src=\"http://bn.globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/standing-outside-the-UN-building-to-show-solidarity.-375x241.jpg\" width=\"375\" height=\"241\" /></a></p>\n<p>联合国声援本次活动</p>\n</div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=235380903265739&#038;set=a.235376876599475.60209.154744967996000&#038;type=3&#038;src=http%3A%2F%2Fsphotos-e.ak.fbcdn.net%2Fhphotos-ak-prn1%2F149988_235380903265739_1334156605_n.jpg&#038;size=960%2C658\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-35476\" alt=\"People RISING at Shilpakala Academy, Dhaka.\" src=\"http://bn.globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/We-are-RISING-at-Shilpakala-Academy-375x257.jpg\" width=\"375\" height=\"257\" /></a></p>\n<p>达卡市Shilpakala学校的人也都站出来支持</p>\n</div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=235732099897286&#038;set=a.154752411328589.35074.154744967996000&#038;type=1&#038;relevant_count=1\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-35477\" alt=\"Bidrohi- an inspiring dance performed by Shadhona at Shilpakala Academy.\" src=\"http://bn.globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/Bidrohi-an-inspiring-dance-performance-by-Shadhona-375x279.jpg\" width=\"375\" height=\"279\" /></a></p>\n<p>Shadhona在Shilpakala学校，表演了一场激励人心的Bidrohi舞蹈</p>\n</div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=235652139905282&#038;set=a.154752411328589.35074.154744967996000&#038;type=1&#038;relevant_count=1\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-35478\" alt=\"5511_235652139905282_969442277_n\" src=\"http://bn.globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/5511_235652139905282_969442277_n-375x210.jpg\" width=\"375\" height=\"210\" /></a></p>\n<p>“亿触即发”在Shahbag世代广场进行抗议时，点燃蜡烛纪念于1971孟加拉独立战争中，饱受暴力的女性</p>\n</div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/OneBillionRisingBangladesh\">“亿触即发”的脸书</a>或<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://obrbangladesh.wordpress.com/\">博客</a>上，有更多的相关照片和故事。</p>\n<div>校对者：Ameli</div>\n<p><span><span>作者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://bn.globalvoicesonline.org/author/pantha/\" title=\"文章导读 পান্থ রহমান রেজা (Pantha)\">পান্থ রহমান রেজা (Pantha)</a></span> · <span>译者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/author/gvzhteam/\" title=\"文章导读 GV 中文化小组\">GV 中文化小组</a></span></span>  · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://bn.globalvoicesonline.org/2013/02/21/35469/\" title=\"阅读原文  bn\">阅读原文  bn</a></span> · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/2013/05/05/12421/#comments\" title=\"则留言\">则留言 (0) </a></span><br />分享: <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.hemidemi.com/user_bookmark/new?title=%E5%AD%9F%E5%8A%A0%E6%8B%89%E5%8F%91%E5%A3%B0%E7%BB%88%E7%BB%93%E5%AF%B9%E5%A5%B3%E6%80%A7%E7%9A%84%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2013%2F05%2F05%2F12421%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=\"HEMiDEMi\"><span>HEMiDEMi</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://myshare.url.com.tw/index.php?func=newurl&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2013%2F05%2F05%2F12421%2F&#038;desc=%E5%AD%9F%E5%8A%A0%E6%8B%89%E5%8F%91%E5%A3%B0%E7%BB%88%E7%BB%93%E5%AF%B9%E5%A5%B3%E6%80%A7%E7%9A%84%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA\" title=\"MyShare\"><span>MyShare</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.shouker.com/\" onclick=\"javascript:var js=document.createElement (\" title=\"Shouker\"><span>Shouker</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2013%2F05%2F05%2F12421%2F\" title=\"facebook\"><span>facebook</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonl